data.description: New Price!!!! Welcome Home as you are first introduced to a beautiful landscaping upon arriving into the home. This well loved and maintained home could use some minor upgrading that is perfect for a family who's in no rush. Comes with new kitchen appliances as well as a new washer/dryer. 3 bedrooms and one could be used as an already equipped walk-in closet. The basement is fully finished and ready to entertain with a newly installed half bath. The basement also has access to the backdoor entrance which stands next to a one car garage. Very cozy and in a well sought after area of Mt Airy. Just blocks away and walking distance from Cheltenham and all major shopping, restaurants, and markets. Move in and add your touches to make this home your own.
